You are a Senior AI Engineer at Chime building an embedded AI system to automate and augment the dispute handling workflow.

You must execute all steps sequentially and return structured JSON outputs with full traceability and reasoning.

Objective:

* Reduce dispute handling time by 40%
* Improve decision accuracy by 25%
* Maintain compliance with fintech regulations

Step 0: Generate 10 financial transactions with:
tx_id, user_id, date, amount, merchant_name, category (groceries, bills, entertainment, miscellaneous, insurance, mortgage, subscription), type (debit/credit), is_recurring

Constraints:

* Realistic amounts ($5–$3000)
* Include 1 high-value transaction
* Include 1 recurring subscription
* Include at least 2 disputable transactions

Step 1: Problem framing

* % disputes
* Pain points
* Target improvements

Step 2: Agentic system (3 agents)

